All organs tested showed positive RT-PCR results, apart from the lymph nodes of patient 2 (Table 2, Table 3
, figure 3
). All non-paraffin-embedded samples were positive for H5 expression. However, paraffin-embedded tissues only showed H5 expression after reamplification of the RT-PCR products. NASBA showed positive results on both types of samples without the need of reamplification.
